stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Draft: Employee starts request
    
    Draft --> Submitted: Employee submits
    Draft --> [*]: Employee cancels
    
    Submitted --> UnderReview: HR opens request
    
    UnderReview --> NeedsInfo: HR requests clarification
    UnderReview --> Approved: HR approves
    UnderReview --> Rejected: HR rejects
    
    NeedsInfo --> Submitted: Employee provides info
    NeedsInfo --> Withdrawn: Employee withdraws
    
    Approved --> Completed: Action completed
    Approved --> [*]: Notification sent
    
    Rejected --> [*]: Notification sent
    Withdrawn --> [*]: Request closed
    Completed --> [*]: Request archived
    
    note right of Submitted
        Status: pending
        Email: Notify HR team
        Visible in HR Dashboard
    end note
    
    note right of UnderReview
        Status: under_review
        Assigned to HR reviewer
        Notes can be added
    end note
    
    note right of Approved
        Status: approved
        Email: Notify employee
        Record reviewer & timestamp
        Update employee calendar
    end note
    
    note right of Rejected
        Status: rejected
        Email: Notify employee with reason
        Record reviewer & timestamp
        Allow resubmission
    end note
